Class EPSG4326

java.lang.Object
  com.nutiteq.projections.Projection
      com.nutiteq.projections.EPSG4326

public class EPSG4326
extends Projection

EPSG:4326 is WGS84, unprojected. Z-coordinate denotes height in meters.
